| Symfony Cache | Redis-backed cache pools |
{% endif %}

### Error Handling

All errors are returned as JSON with a consistent envelope (see [api-contract.md](api-contract.md)). Symfony's `kernel.exception` event listener normalizes exceptions before they reach the client. HTTP status codes follow RFC 9110.

