{% if use_rabbitmq %}
## Asynchronous Messaging (Symfony Messenger + RabbitMQ)

Long-running tasks (email sending, report generation, webhooks) are dispatched as messages via Symfony Messenger and processed asynchronously by a consumer worker.

```
Controller  ──dispatch()──►  MessageBus  ──►  RabbitMQ exchange
                                                      │
                                              Worker process
                                              (bin/console messenger:consume)
                                                      │
                                              MessageHandler
```

The frontend does not interact with RabbitMQ directly. It may poll an endpoint or use a WebSocket channel to receive completion status.
{% endif %}

