{% if use_ci %}
## CI/CD Pipeline

GitHub Actions runs on every push:

```
.github/workflows/
├── api.yml     # PHP linting + PHPUnit
└── web.yml     # TypeScript check + Vitest{% if test_strategy == "full-pyramid" %} + Playwright{% endif %}
```

**Deployment sequence (enforced by CI gates):**
1. Run API tests - must pass before deploying API
2. Deploy API and run migrations
3. Run frontend tests - must pass before deploying frontend
4. Deploy frontend

This order ensures the database is always in the state the new API version expects before the new frontend version goes live.
{% endif %}

